Welcome! Intellij is an integrated development environment (IDE), which is used for writing and testing code. There are
various different IDEs that can be used for programming and you are free to choose whatever IDE you want, this course,
however, is written with Intellij features in mind to help beginner programmer overcome non-programming related
obstacles. It is strongly recommended that you use Intellij for this course.

Okay! Lets get right into some Intellij basics. Open the lesson_00/exercise/ExerciseUsingIntellij.txt file
